config BR2_PACKAGE_HD_IDLE
	bool "Hard disk idle spin-down utility"
	help
	  hd-idle is a utility program for spinning-down external disks after a
	  period of idle time. Sine most external IDE disk enclosures don't support
	  setting the IDE idle timer, a program like hd-idle is required to spin
	  down idle disks automatically.

	  http://hd-idle.sf.net
